# Social publishing — each connection's access_token is supplied per-user via
# POST /api/connections (not a server-side secret). You'll still need your
# own developer app registered with each platform before OAuth works:
#   Meta (FB Page/Group/Instagram): developers.facebook.com — note
#     publish_to_groups requires separate App Review approval
#   X: developer.x.com
#   LinkedIn: developer.linkedin.com — organization posting needs
#     w_organization_social scope + Community Management API access
#   Pinterest: developers.pinterest.com
#   TikTok: developers.tiktok.com — Content Posting API needs its own
#     audit/approval beyond standard developer registration
